    <item>
      <title>1850 亿美元债券销售狂潮吸引渴望收益的买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/frenzy-of-sales-in-red-hot-debt-market-draws-yield-hungry-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[借款人正以前所未有的速度涌入全球债务市场，试图利用渴望信贷的管理者的需求。这些管理者资金充裕，已经导致公司债券利差降至近 30 年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/frenzy-of-sales-in-red-hot-debt-market-draws-yield-hungry-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
